name: Joe
string:
Hey, you must be
a newcomer. I'm
Joe. Nice to
meet you. The
morning fair is
held here on
Tuesdays and
Saturdays from
6AM till 9AM.
You can sell
your products
there. Let me
know if you want
to join us.

name: Joe
string:

early? Do you
want to join the
morning fair?

 Yes          No<ask>

name: Joe

is over today.

name: Joe
string:
